<div>
  <div class='text-center'>
    <h1>歯ブラシを登録しよう！</h1>
    <li>通常の歯ブラシ以外に、電動歯ブラシや子ども用歯ブラシも検索できます。</li>
  </div>
  <div class="container" >
    <div class="search-box">
      <%= form_with url: new_toothbrush_path, method: :get, local: true do |f| %>
        <div class="form-group">
            <%= f.text_field :keyword, value: params[:keyword], placeholder: '歯ブラシの名前を入力して楽天市場から検索', class: "form-control" , style: "width:75%" %>
            <%= f.submit '製品を検索', class: "form-control btn btn-success", style: "width:75%" %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="line-it-button" data-lang="ja" data-type="friend" data-env="REAL" data-count="true" data-home="true" data-lineId="<%= ENV['LINE_OFFICIAL_ID'] %>" style="display: none;"></div>
    <script src="https://www.line-website.com/social-plugins/js/thirdparty/loader.min.js" async="async" defer="defer"></script>
  </div>
</div>